<h2 class="bold font-l">Why Does This Happen To Me?</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Susan finds herself in many fanservice situations during the Fantastic Four movies, much to her distress. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ReluctantFanserviceGirl" class='trope-example-link'>Reluctant Fanservice Girl</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
